StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [IsSignedTrainingProvided]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@TrainingProvidedID uniqueidentifier
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT COUNT(*) As Total FROM USMC.TrainingProvided WHERE ID = @TrainingProvidedID AND RecruiterSignatureID IS NOT NULL END
